---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy | Linda Della Industries" description="How Linda Della Industries handles website inquiry data.">
  <SiteHeader />
  <main id="main-content" class="legal-page section-shell">
    <article class="shell legal-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span>Policy</span> Effective July 16, 2026</p>
      <h1>Privacy, in plain language.</h1>
      <p class="legal-lede">The inquiry form asks for the information listed below so Linda Della Industries can evaluate and answer your request. Please do not submit passwords, financial records, health information, legal case details, government identifiers, or other sensitive or regulated data.</p>
      <h2>What the inquiry form collects</h2><p>Name, email, optional business or organization, optional website, the workflow description you choose to provide, and your consent to be contacted.</p>
      <h2>Why it is used</h2><p>Linda Della Industries uses inquiry information to evaluate fit, respond, and maintain ordinary business correspondence. Linda Della does not sell inquiry information or use it to make decisions about you solely through an automated process.</p>
      <h2>Form delivery</h2><p>Website submissions are processed by <a href="https://formsubmit.co/privacy.pdf">FormSubmit</a> and delivered to a Google-hosted email account. FormSubmit receives the information in the form so it can provide that service and states that submissions are archived for 30 days. If you prefer not to use FormSubmit, you may email <a href="mailto:willdoraniv@gmail.com">willdoraniv@gmail.com</a> directly, although that email will still be processed through the sender’s and recipient’s email providers.</p>
      <h2>Retention and requests</h2><p>Inquiry submissions and related email correspondence are retained in the business email account for correspondence and ordinary business or legal recordkeeping. You may request access, correction, or deletion by emailing the address below. A request may be limited where retention is needed for security, dispute resolution, or legal obligations.</p>
      <h2>Hosting, analytics, and technical data</h2><p>This site does not include analytics code or advertising pixels installed by Linda Della Industries. It is hosted on GitHub Pages, and the inquiry form uses FormSubmit and a Google-hosted mailbox. Those providers may receive technical information such as IP address, browser details, request time, and security signals under their own privacy policies.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2><p>William Doran IV<br />Linda Della Industries, a service name used by William Doran IV<br />Baltimore, Maryland<br /><a href="mailto:willdoraniv@gmail.com">willdoraniv@gmail.com</a></p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>
